  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\n        \n\n    \n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003cp\u003eMost roommate rants are the stuff of\u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/40279045/ive-been-warned-by-my-manager-to-not-to-go-to-hr-because-they-wont-care-about-petty-drama-hotel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e urban legend: wild tales \u003c/a\u003eof shared bathrooms slowly turning into biohazards,\u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/40182789/21-hr-safe-corporate-clapbacks-that-professionally-prompt-people-to-pivot-their-pettines-and-back\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e heated debates over \u003c/a\u003ewhat exactly counts as \u0026#34;quiet hours,\u0026#34; and the \u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/40182789/21-hr-safe-corporate-clapbacks-that-professionally-prompt-people-to-pivot-their-pettines-and-back\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003ecrisis triggered by discovering\u003c/a\u003e just how many decibels a single bowl of cereal can produce at 2 AM. These complaints aren\u0026#39;t just cliché—they\u0026#39;re an ancient rite of passage, a way for adults to process the unavoidable truth that nobody on earth would choose to have a roommate if rent weren\u0026#39;t more terrifying than the roommate themselves. Let\u0026#39;s face it: deep down, everyone just wants (or rather, is brutally forced by their bank account) to have another human around to halve the pain of paying for shelter.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThat’s what makes this story such a fascinating upgrade from the old “she left hair in the drain” saga. Here we have a roommate who dared to dream bigger—she skipped the hygiene debates, breezed past the decibel wars, and went for the gold: simply stopped paying altogether. Why argue over whether her boyfriend can nap on your couch when she’s decided to stage a one-woman rent strike? Now that’s innovation in the art of cohabitation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e01\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u0026#34;AITA for refusing to pay my broke roommate\u0026#39;s rent again, causing her to move out suddenly?\u0026#34;\u003c/h2\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10498028288/h0B1D2F42/refused-and-told-her-wasnt-bank-she-called-heartles\" id=\"_r_a_10498028288\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" alt=\"\u0026#34;I refused and told her I wasn\u0026#39;t a bank. She called me heartles❞\" title=\"\u0026#34;AITA for refusing to pay my broke roommate\u0026#39;s rent again, causing her to move out suddenly?\u0026#34;\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e02\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497796096/h34AF687C/with-my-roommate-25f-been-living-together-nearly-year-and-s-been-mostly-fine-until-recently\" id=\"_r_a_10497796096\" width=\"429\" height=\"249\" alt=\"I (24F) am a struggling grad student sharing an apartment with my roommate (25F). We\u0026#39;ve been living together for nearly a year, and it\u0026#39;s been mostly fine until recently.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e03\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497796352/h6CC7333C/pay-her-half-rent-been-sympathetic-covered-some-utilities-and-even-bought-groceries-share-last\" id=\"_r_a_10497796352\" width=\"436\" height=\"240\" alt=\"My roommate lost her job two months ago and has been struggling to pay her half of the rent. I\u0026#39;ve been sympathetic, covered some utilities, and even bought groceries we share. Last\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e04\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497796608/hE44A4FEB/her-portion-rent-just-this-once-while-she-looks-work-agreed-because-had-some-savings-though-tight\" id=\"_r_a_10497796608\" width=\"430\" height=\"232\" alt=\"month, she asked if I could cover her portion of the rent \u0026#34;just this once\u0026#34; while she looks for work. I agreed because I had some savings, though it was tight for me.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e05\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10498043648/hB2B496A1\" id=\"_r_a_10498043648\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10498043648\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e06\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497795840/h6CC6E064/she-tearfully-asked-if-could-cover-her-rent-again-promising-shed-pay-back-as-soon-as-she-gets\" id=\"_r_a_10497795840\" width=\"454\" height=\"202\" alt=\"This month rolls around, and she still doesn\u0026#39;t have a job. Yesterday she tearfully asked if I could cover her rent again, promising she\u0026#39;d pay me back \u0026#34;as soon as she gets\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e07\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497795328/h25BAB814/her-couldnt-afford-keep-covering-her-and-suggested-she-reach-out-her-parents-who-know-are-well-off\" id=\"_r_a_10497795328\" width=\"418\" height=\"213\" alt=\"back on her feet.\u0026#34; I told her I couldn\u0026#39;t afford to keep covering for her and suggested she reach out to her parents (who I know are well-off).\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e08\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497795584/hF66E5D00/knew-she-struggling-and-shed-have-leave-city-and-her-boyfriend-she-begged-help-just-one-more-time\" id=\"_r_a_10497795584\" width=\"435\" height=\"286\" alt=\"She broke down, saying her parents would make her move back home if they knew she was struggling, and she\u0026#39;d have to leave the city and her boyfriend. She begged me to help \u0026#34;just one more time.\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e09\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497797120/hC1CA3C4E/figure-something-out-because-wasnt-bank-she-called-heartless-and-said-real-friend-would-help-crisis\" id=\"_r_a_10497797120\" width=\"462\" height=\"205\" alt=\"I refused and told her she needed to figure something out because | wasn\u0026#39;t a bank. She called me heartless and said \u0026#34;a real friend would help in a crisis.\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10498043136/h05E318CA/not-a-bank\" id=\"_r_a_10498043136\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10498043136\" title=\"NOT a Bank\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497797376/hF7EFB29C/woke-up-find-her-stuff-gone-and-note-saying-shes-moving-with-her-boyfriend-she-also-took-our\" id=\"_r_a_10497797376\" width=\"427\" height=\"166\" alt=\"This morning, I woke up to find her stuff gone and a note saying she\u0026#39;s moving in with her boyfriend. She also took our\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497796864/h3556971F/microwave-and-coffee-maker-which-bought-together-and-left-with-full-rent-due-three-days\" id=\"_r_a_10497796864\" width=\"451\" height=\"162\" alt=\"microwave and coffee maker (which we bought together) and left me with the full rent due in three days.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497797888/hDADAC1B0/set-boundaries-others-think-shouldve-helped-her-one-last-time-since-now-stuck-with-full-rent-anyway\" id=\"_r_a_10497797888\" width=\"450\" height=\"219\" alt=\"My other friends are split - some say I was right to set boundaries, others think I should\u0026#39;ve helped her \u0026#34;one last time\u0026#34; since now I\u0026#39;m stuck with the full rent anyway.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497797632/hB9FB1488/aita-refusing-cover-my-unemployed-roommates-rent-second-time\" id=\"_r_a_10497797632\" width=\"451\" height=\"169\" alt=\"AITA for refusing to cover my unemployed roommate\u0026#39;s rent a second time?\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497798144/h6C6EE509/and-community-property-fact-she-moved-with-her-boyfriend-says-she-is-willing-help-pay-his-expenses\" id=\"_r_a_10497798144\" width=\"385\" height=\"498\" alt=\"False_Garden_3468 I would definitely call her parents and explain that their daughter ran out and owes gou 3 months\u0026#39; rent and community property. The fact that she moved in with her boyfriend says she is willing to help pay his expenses.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497799680/h08CA4AA6/small-claims-court-and-more-often-than-not-they-also-get-damages-which-totals-more-than-owed\" id=\"_r_a_10497799680\" width=\"379\" height=\"336\" alt=\"Also, tell her parents know that you would be recovering past due expenses through small claims court, and more often than not, they also get damages, which totals more than what was owed.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e17\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497799168/h2104B3AB/dont-owe-her-protection-her-parents-shes-an-adult-who-owes-and-needs-pay-nta\" id=\"_r_a_10497799168\" width=\"391\" height=\"177\" alt=\"You don\u0026#39;t owe her protection from her parents. She\u0026#39;s an adult who owes and needs to pay. Nta\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e18\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497798656/h844AFF28/months-rent-and-whatever-notice-period-she-should-have-paid-send-proof-paid-all-rent-last-month\" id=\"_r_a_10497798656\" width=\"526\" height=\"318\" alt=\"Pikelets_for_tea NTA. Contact her parents and ask them to reimburse you for last month\u0026#39;s rent and for whatever notice period she should have paid. Send proof you paid all the rent last month.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e19\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497798912/hA1BF49F8/might-pay-is-worth-try-certainly-satisfying-revenge-edit-and-lot-quicker-than-small-claims-court\" id=\"_r_a_10497798912\" width=\"367\" height=\"237\" alt=\"They might pay you, it is worth a try. Certainly satisfying revenge. Edit: And a lot quicker than small claims court.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497798400/h96909AC8/no-adhesiveness-if-shes-on-lease-shes-still-on-hook-her-portion-whether-she-lives-there-or-not\" id=\"_r_a_10497798400\" width=\"348\" height=\"292\" alt=\"No-Adhesiveness If she\u0026#39;s on the lease she\u0026#39;s still on the hook for her portion whether she lives there or not.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e21\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497799424/hA4BA4C16/last-time-so-do-and-friends-know-if-this-time-she-asks-rent-money-is-actual-last-time-dont\" id=\"_r_a_10497799424\" width=\"379\" height=\"357\" alt=\"solardune NTA. Last time was supposedly \u0026#34;the last time\u0026#34; so how do you, and your friends, know if this time she asks for rent money is the actual last time? You don\u0026#39;t.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e22\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497799936/h6E6DC78B/friend-is-an-adult-who-needs-manage-her-own-money-helped-her-once-and-good-but-right-not-bank\" id=\"_r_a_10497799936\" width=\"385\" height=\"241\" alt=\"Your friend is an adult who needs to manage her own money. You helped her once and that was good of you, but you\u0026#39;re right, you\u0026#39;re not a bank.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n            \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e23\u003c/span\u003e\n                            \u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10497800192/h8E479CC0/she-bailed-on-rent-and-took-shared-stuff-so-dont-feel-guilty-setting-boundary-she-didnt-respect\" id=\"_r_a_10497800192\" width=\"405\" height=\"445\" alt=\"AmeliaLunar you\u0026#39;re not a bank, and it\u0026#39;s not your job to carry someone who won\u0026#39;t find a way to help themselves. She bailed on the rent and took shared stuff, so don\u0026#39;t feel guilty for setting a boundary she didn\u0026#39;t respect.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n            \u003cp\u003eStay up to date by following us on \u003ca href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FailBlog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eFacebook\u003c/a\u003e!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                \u003ch2\u003eTags\u003c/h2\u003e\n        \n\n            \n\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll dow